# Tools & Workflow

- Find code by behavior or symbol: `semble search` first; use grep only for exhaustive literal matches.
- Related code: `semble find-related <file> <line> [path]`
- Fallback if semble missing: `uvx --from "semble[mcp]" semble`
- Web QA/automation: `agent-browser` — open URL, `snapshot -i`, interact via refs, re-snapshot after navigation.
- Library APIs and patterns: context7 MCP/CLI — verify current docs before implementing.
- **web-vite UI:** `Page → Container → Component`; tRPC only in `components/{domain}/hooks/` or `src/hooks/`. Run `pnpm check:web-vite-data-layer` before merge. See [`apps/web-vite/ARCHITECTURE.md`](../../apps/web-vite/ARCHITECTURE.md).
